@letsgo2022 Through his own account, I think he, as a young man who was once sought by the National Security Bureau for resisting Xi Jinping, was under great mental pressure.
He thinks that it is not his fault that he was treated this way, but that he was hurt.
In fact, in recent years, we have seen that many democrats who have experienced persecution and imprisonment have such trauma. We need to understand what caused all this.
